commit.message:
build: set minimum required CMake to 3.5

Avoids:
```bash
CMake Deprecation Warning at CMakeLists.txt:1 (cmake_minimum_required):
  Compatibility with CMake < 3.5 will be removed from a future version of
  CMake.

  Update the VERSION argument <min> value or use a ...<max> suffix to tell
  CMake that the project does not need compatibility with older versions.
```

commit.message:
natpmpc.c Print usage at once

This will make the resulting binary smaller

define _DEFAULT_SOURCE instead of _BSD_SOURCE

`_BSD_SOURCE` is deprecated:
```bash
  148 | # warning "_BSD_SOURCE and _SVID_SOURCE are deprecated, use _DEFAULT_SOURCE"
```

See also:
https://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Feature-Test-Macros.html
https://lwn.net/Articles/590381/
